  "text": "Chronic urticaria e mechanism of chronic spontaneous urticaria (CU) is still incompletely understood. About half of the patients have autoantibodies against FcεRI and a few against IgE. CU sera activate resting basophils of normal donors to upregulate CD63 and CD203c. BAT may replace the autologous serum skin test (ASST) [CITATION_1] .",
